cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper is about video super-resolution, which is a computer vision task. Therefore, cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also proposes a deep learning approach, which involves training a neural network, making cs.MM (Multimedia) another likely sub-category. The paper also discusses the efficiency and accuracy of the proposed approach, which suggests that it may fall under cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper involves image processing, which may fall under cs.GR (Graphics).
